{"tid":808511,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"北海道6.8級地震係咪前震？","createTime":"2018-09-06T11:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T12:41:12.000Z","uid":197125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e954eb3350307ff1152c4929bae86313b465ca9","tid":808511,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:20:21.000Z","msg":"通常主震完後會發生一系列嘅餘震，而且唔少次都有五級以上，但今次震完後只有兩次五級以上餘震，有啲懷疑仲有大能量未釋放出嚟，所以我估今次係前震而主震仲未發生。當然，最好係我估錯啦，天佑日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5df211e895f889b05d728c021f2adcec7bba47","tid":808511,"uid":124107,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"022ab6dc367ab3f4c5097e433c279767e0220aa1","tid":808511,"uid":55408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"換個角度諗有冇可能係大阪震完影響到北海道地底股能量，從而提前釋放出黎，所以先唔太高震度呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識9up下 天祐日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d906e9add37595cda005a20282c4ae6cff131521","tid":808511,"uid":124107,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dec7f1c68dfa99c96e7f320b8444a85d70ea4385","tid":808511,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"黎緊有次8級"},{"pid":"ee6953a9ec17c9340eb0c816fb3abba2c701c50b","tid":808511,"uid":106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"022ab6dc367ab3f4c5097e433c279767e0220aa1","tid":808511,"uid":55408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"換個角度諗有冇可能係大阪震完影響到北海道地底股能量，從而提前釋放出黎，所以先唔太高震度呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識9up下 天祐日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:16:19.000Z","msg":"大阪幾時有震過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1cee841ac35ab24f991242a66683634e7477db","tid":808511,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"無錯，如果有日本FD叫佢地快D走"},{"pid":"1dfc8b241c866a33f044dcb9a0ea8520861534b3","tid":808511,"uid":163783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"如果未係主震，今晚聽日高危"},{"pid":"0aaf721acde90232aaf16cb9a3d614cfd3487238","tid":808511,"uid":38255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"熊本前震 M6.5<br />\n之後有下「餘震」M6.4<br />\n然後主震 M7.3<br />\n<br />\n反而係餘震太密太強先係主震未到既先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然每次都唔同模式，只係以舊例去試睇，無話唔係熊本個模式就一定無主震在後既可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e73e5c01dfaec95fd873271586532204d7d169","tid":808511,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"022ab6dc367ab3f4c5097e433c279767e0220aa1","tid":808511,"uid":55408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"換個角度諗有冇可能係大阪震完影響到北海道地底股能量，從而提前釋放出黎，所以先唔太高震度呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識9up下 天祐日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:34:26.000Z","msg":"差太遠，加上斷層唔同，唔係太關事"},{"pid":"784e92630cbd6567decd3bed0f236c80f08766b9","tid":808511,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n熊本前震既餘震 3個鐘就過百，一日半後有近350次餘震，然後真主震發生<br />\n<br />\n6月大阪果次，主震一日半後只有35次餘震左右，之後餘震1日兩三次咁無「真主震」<br />\n<br />\n今次北海道 半日70次餘震，介乎兩者之間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家兩個鐘3次既水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔作任何判斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}